Class YamlHtmlDumper

java.lang.Object
org.krmdemo.techlabs.core.dump.yaml.YamlHtmlDumper
All Implemented Interfaces:
TreeDumper
public class YamlHtmlDumper extends Object implements TreeDumper
Implementation of TreeDumper that dumps into the passed PrintStream the tree of a YAML logical structure in HTML target format (HTML-CSS is coming soon).
